16 // V3Randomize's Transformations:
17 //
18 // Each randomize() method call:
19 // Mark class of object on which randomize() is called
20 // Mark all classes that inherit from previously marked classed
21 // Mark all classes whose instances are randomized member variables of marked classes
22 // Each marked class:
23 // * define a virtual randomize() method that randomizes its random variables
24 // Each call to randomize():
25 // * define __Vrandwith### functions for randomize() calls with inline constraints and
26 // put then into randomized classes
27 // * replace calls to randomize() that use inline constraints with calls to __Vrandwith###
28 // functions
29 //
